---
title: Prawn Caesar Salad with roasted chickpeas
description: A fresh take on a restaurant classic, this prawn and chickpea Ceasar is anything but ordinary!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R12_W48_IE_IEXQS31398-2_Main_high-5d210435.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/66e181c9ab5003dbd1aa1ac3-en-IE.pdf
